WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:07.520
He can, but I can't.

2
00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:08.190
Really?

3
00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:12.180
Just answer me,

4
00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:13.340
why do you like him?

5
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:17.620
Today's been the most thrilling, unlucky, and embarrassing day of my life.

8
00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:24.320
I just wanted to save another student's life.

11
00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:26.540
Why am I forced to go through all this?

12
00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:28.820
Did I really do something wrong?

13
00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:31.760
Jining Ling, answer me,

14
00:00:32.080 --> 00:00:33.500
why do you like him?

15
00:00:34.820 --> 00:00:38.200
He is sunny, talented, elegant, gentle and considerate.

17
00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:41.780
Unlike you, cruel and ruthless, usurping another's dignity to play the father.

21
00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:49.580
You think you are me, owning everything, but you just built your so-called empire on violence and petty crime.

26
00:00:50.020 --> 00:00:53.400
Jining Ling, is that how you see me?

